data.description: Price Reduction to $419,800!! Beautiful Ranch Style house in a Cul-de-Sac with privacy in a FAYETTEVILLE GREAT LOCATION!!!. No HOA. Over 3,000 Sq. Ft of livable space including a Finished Basement. 3 bd - 2 ba in the main level and 2 bd - 1 ba in the basement. House is recently painted & has several upgrades. Eat-in Island Kitchen. Separate dining room. Living room with a fireplace. A loft upstairs (third level) with a storage closet. Has a large Yard and a Covered Back Porch. The house has several Storage spaces. 2 Car Garage with room for a workshop and another storage room. Circular driveway. Close to Fayetteville Pavilion, several restaurants, grocery stores, shops and more!!
